id="post-3392" class="post-3392 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-art category-direct-action category-mind-space tag-bike tag-charlottetown tag-p-e-i tag-people tag-street tag-urban"><h2 class="entry-title"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2012/08/01/charlottetown-transforms-a-street-for-people/" title="Permalink to Charlottetown Transforms a Street for People" rel="bookmark">Charlottetown Transforms a Street for People</a></h2><div
class="entry-meta"> <span
class="entry-date" title="2012/08/01 11:53 am"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2012/08/01/charlottetown-transforms-a-street-for-people/" title="Charlottetown Transforms a Street for People" rel="bookmark">2012/08/01 11:53 am</a></span><span
class="entry-meta-sep"> / </span><span
class="entry-author author vcard"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/author/administrator/" title="by Adam Clare" rel="author">Adam Clare</a></span></div><div
class="entry-content clearfix"><p>Residents of Charlottetown, P.E.I. decided to make their city nicer, more sustainable, and more fun by transforming one of their streets from car-dominated to people-friendly. They&#8217;ve made a great video showing what they did and hopefully it&#8217;ll inspire other communities to realize that streets are for people and we should use public space to celebrate the public.</p><p><iframe
width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/qXpYlgCH5Ps" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote><p>People were really excited to join in on the one-day project, says one participant in the video. &#8220;People would just be walking by and like, &#8220;Oh, what&#8217;s going on?&#8221; I would tell them, &#8220;We&#8217;re transforming a street, do you want to take part?&#8221; All of a sudden, they were grabbing paint or chalk.&#8221;</p></blockquote><p><em>Thanks to Kathryn</em>! Who found it <a
href="http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2012/08/01/transform-a-street-charlottetown_n_1717409.html">Huffington Post</a>.</p><div
class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-1111807-3392-53838c8549dd6' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/#blog_id=1111807&amp;post_id=3392&amp;origin=www.thingsaregood.com&amp;obj_id=1111807-3392-53838c8549dd6' data-name='like-post-frame-1111807-3392-53838c8549dd6'><h3 class='sd-title'>Like this:</h3><div
